metadata.name: Alpha Blocks #1
metadata.description: Our idea is to create an exclusive, low-supply 555 collection as our genesis collection. We want to build a solid core community and alpha group with our genesis holders, who will be provided with immense benefits. The genesis collection is the start of our vision, combining challenging work from our team, NFTs & alpha groups, with a single goal in mind: make the collection worthwhile and reward our early investors. The game itself is already in development.
